lead_paragraph: Cowboys owner Jerry Jones has acknowledged speaking with the NFL's special counsel for domestic violence investigations, and rookie running back Ezekiel Elliott said he was interviewed by the league this season about an abuse claim made against him.

headline.print_headline: Dallas Owner Spoke to NFL Counsel About Elliott Abuse Probe
